        "range": "Self.",
        "overview": {
          "base": "You gain a benefit that you can expend in one of following ways of your choosing.\n<dl><dt>Attack Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Attack_abilities\" title=\"Category:Attack abilities\" target=\"_blank\">attack</a> you make is <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Keyword:AV0\" title=\"Keyword:AV0\" target=\"_blank\">AV0</a>.</dd>\n<dt>Check Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next time you <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Ability:Attempt_Check\" title=\"Ability:Attempt Check\" target=\"_blank\">Attempt Check</a> you do so with <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Advantage\" title=\"Core:Advantage\" target=\"_blank\">advantage</a>.</dd></dl>\nYou may only choose one benefit per use of Combo.",
          "proficient": "The list of possible benefits you can choose from is expanded to include the following.\n<dl><dt>Block Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Block_abilities\" title=\"Category:Block abilities\" target=\"_blank\">block</a> you make may be done with <i>2</i> <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Equipment\" title=\"Category:Equipment\" target=\"_blank\">items</a> instead of 1. You add the <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Block_Interaction\" title=\"Core:Block Interaction\" target=\"_blank\">BV</a> for both.</dd>\n<dt>Condition Combo</dt>\n<dd>Instead of rolling <span class=\"dice\" data-full-roll=\"2d4\" data-quick-roll=\"2d4\" data-type=\"endCon\">[[/roll 2d4]]</span> to end some <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Effects\" title=\"Category:Effects\" target=\"_blank\">effect</a>, you may roll either <span class=\"dice\" data-full-roll=\"1d4\" data-quick-roll=\"1d4\" data-type=\"endCon\">[[/roll 1d4]]</span> or <span class=\"dice\" data-full-roll=\"3d4\" data-quick-roll=\"3d4\" data-type=\"endCon\">[[/roll 3d4]]</span> (you choose). The effect ends if any of the dice roll a 4.</dd>\n<dt>Feat Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next time you make a <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Feat_abilities\" title=\"Category:Feat abilities\" target=\"_blank\">feat save</a>, you do so with <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Advantage\" title=\"Core:Advantage\" target=\"_blank\">advantage</a>.</dd>\n<dt>Resistance Combo</dt>\n<dd>The next time you make a <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Resistance_effects\" title=\"Category:Resistance effects\" target=\"_blank\">resistance save</a>, you do so with <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Advantage\" title=\"Core:Advantage\" target=\"_blank\">advantage</a>.<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r8437\">.mw-parser-output .ability-bar-title *{color:var(--color-base)}.mw-parser-output .es-wording-container .ability-bar-title *{color:inherit}</style></dd></dl>",
